text: David Carr (born 1 October 1995 in Wigton) is an English professional darts player who competes in the British Darts Organisation events. ==Career== Carr has played professional darts since 2014, but did not place higher than Final 16 until Scottish Open in 2016, where he made it to the Semi Final. Here he lost 1-5 to Dean Reynolds.
